# Project Context for Claude

This directory contains a complete project for refactoring the manual testing infrastructure.

## Quick Start

1. Read README.md for project overview
2. Review TRACKER.md for current status and task list
3. Read research-findings.md for supporting evidence
4. Review implementation-plan.md for technical details

